EN: Please enter at the designated time.

ZH: 入场券需要提前购买。
EN: Tickets need to be purchased in advance for entry.

ZH: 您需要展示您的入场证明。
EN: You need to show your entry proof.

ZH: 请在门口入场。
EN: Please enter at the gate.

ZH: 他因为没有入场券而被拒绝入场。
EN: He was denied entry because he didn't have a ticket.

ZH: 请勿在未经许可的情况下入场。
EN: Do not enter without permission.

ZH: 这是唯一的入场门。
EN: This is the only entrance.

ZH: 入场后请保持安静。
EN: Please keep quiet after entering.

ZH: 入场人数已经达到限制。
EN: The number of people entering has reached the limit.

ZH: 我们希望您享受入场体验。
EN: We hope you enjoy your entry experience.

ZH: 每周六晚入场免费。
EN: Entry is free on Saturday nights.

ZH: 入场要求所有参与者年满18岁以上。
EN: Entry requires all participants to be 18 years or older.

ZH: 请妥善保管您的入场证件。
EN: Please keep your entry documents safe.

ZH: 请在比赛开始前10分钟入场。
EN: Please enter 10 minutes before the game starts.

ZH: 入场时请出示身份证件。
EN: Please show your ID when entering.

ZH: 不准携带食品入场。
EN: No food allowed to be brought in for entry.

ZH: 他兴高采烈地入场。
EN: He entered enthusiastically.

ZH: 入场之后请注意自己的随身物品。
EN: Please watch your belongings after entering.

ZH: 入场费用必须在入场之前支付。
EN: Entry fees must be paid before entering.

ZH: 入场之后请将手机调至静音。
EN: Please switch your phone to silent mode after entering.
